    <div class="container">
      <header>
        <img class="logo" src="http://136.228.141.22/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Flogo.198a873d.png&w=64&q=75" alt="Logo SBS" />
        <h1>SBS Booking Confirmation</h1>
      </header>
      <div class="content">
        <p class="details">
          Hi, <span class="importantText"><%=name%></span><br />
          We are pleased to confirm your recent booking with Shuttle Bus.
        </p>

        <p class="details">
          <div class="detailItem">
            <span style="font-size: medium; font-weight: bold; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, Tahoma, sans-serif;">Details of Your Booking:</span>
          </div>
          <div class="detailItem">
            <span class="detaileNameText">Departure</span>
            <span class="detailInfoText">: <%=departure%></span>
          </div>
          <div class="detailItem">
            <span class="detaileNameText">Departure Date</span>
            <span class="detailInfoText">: <%=departureDate%></span>
          </div>
          <div class="detailItem">
            <span class="detaileNameText">Departure Time</span>
            <span class="detailInfoText">: <%=departureTime%></span>
          </div>
          <div class="detailItem">
            <span class="detaileNameText">Date of Booking</span>
            <span class="detailInfoText">: <%=booking_date%></span>
          </div>
          <div class="detailItem">
            <span class="detaileNameText">Pick Up at</span>
            <span class="detailInfoText">: <%=pickup%></span>
          </div>
          <div class="detailItem">
            <span class="detaileNameText">Drop off at</span>
            <span class="detailInfoText">: <%=drop%></span>
          </div>
        </p>
        <p class="note">
          This email serves as a confirmation of your booking. If you have any questions or concerns, feel free to reach out to us at
          <a href="mailto:<%=sbsTeam%>" class="linkText">email</a>
        </p>
        <p class="note">
          Please note that this is a confirmation email, and you can simply disregard it if everything is in order.
        </p>
      </div>
      <footer>
        <p>Best regards, Shuttle Bus Team</p>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
